---
const manifestoHref = '#manifesto';
---

<html lang="pt-BR" class="bg-slate-950">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="Chapa Apolo: a missão de fundar o CACOMP começou. Um novo salto para a Computação do Piauí."
		/>
		<meta name="theme-color" content="#020617" />
		<title>Chapa Apolo | Lançamento CACOMP</title>

		<style is:global>
			:root {
				color-scheme: dark;
				background-color: #020617;
			}

			* {
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			html {
				background: #020617;
				scroll-behavior: smooth;
			}

			body {
				margin: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				background: #020617;
				color: #e2e8f0;
				font-family:
					Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
					sans-serif;
				-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
				text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
			}

			::selection {
				background: #3b82f6;
				color: #020617;
			}

			.sr-only {
				position: absolute;
				width: 1px;
				height: 1px;
				padding: 0;
				margin: -1px;
				overflow: hidden;
				clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
				white-space: nowrap;
				border-width: 0;
			}

			.hero-shell {
				position: relative;
				display: flex;
				min-height: 100vh;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				overflow: hidden;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.hero-bg {
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background:
					radial-gradient(circle at 50% 18%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.16), transparent 34%),
					radial-gradient(circle at 50% 115%, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1), transparent 28%),
					linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.96) 0%, rgba(2, 6, 23, 1) 100%);
			}

			.hero-glow {
				position: absolute;
				border-radius: 9999px;
				filter: blur(72px);
				opacity: 0.6;
				pointer-events: none;
			}

			.hero-glow--top {
				top: 10%;
				left: 50%;
				width: 14rem;
				height: 14rem;
				transform: translateX(-50%);
				background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.24);
			}

			.hero-glow--bottom {
				right: -4rem;
				bottom: 3rem;
				width: 12rem;
				height: 12rem;
				background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
			}

			.hero-grid {
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
				width: min(100%, 74rem);
				margin-inline: auto;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
			}

			.eyebrow {
				margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
				border-radius: 9999px;
				background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
				padding: 0.72rem 1rem;
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				letter-spacing: 0.28em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #60a5fa;
				backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
			}

			.hero-title {
				margin: 0;
				max-width: 16ch;
				font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
				font-weight: 800;
				line-height: 1.04;
				letter-spacing: -0.04em;
				text-wrap: balance;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #dbeafe 48%, #60a5fa 100%);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				background-clip: text;
				color: transparent;
			}

			.hero-subtitle {
				margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
				max-width: 40rem;
				font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 3vw, 1.375rem);
				line-height: 1.7;
				color: #94a3b8;
				text-wrap: balance;
			}

			.cta-wrap {
				margin-top: 2.5rem;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}

			.cta-primary {
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 0.75rem;
				border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.24);
				border-radius: 1.25rem;
				background: #2563eb;
				padding: 1.125rem 1.75rem;
				font-size: 1rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				line-height: 1.2;
				color: #ffffff;
				text-decoration: none;
				box-shadow:
					0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.45),
					0 0 0 rgba(37, 99, 235, 0);
				transition:
					transform 0.3s ease,
					background-color 0.3s ease,
					box-shadow 0.3s ease,
					border-color 0.3s ease;
			}

			.cta-primary:hover {
				background: #3b82f6;
				transform: scale(1.05);
				box-shadow:
					0 0 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4),
					0 22px 55px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.45);
			}

			.cta-primary:focus-visible {
				outline: none;
				box-shadow:
					0 0 0 4px rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.52),
					0 0 0 8px rgba(2, 6, 23, 1),
					0 0 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
			}

			.terrain-shell {
				position: relative;
				padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
				background:
					radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08), transparent 42%),
					linear-gradient(180deg, #020617 0%, #0f172a 100%);
			}

			.terrain-copy {
				margin: 0 auto;
				max-width: 48rem;
				font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.65rem);
				line-height: 1.85;
				text-align: center;
				text-wrap: balance;
				color: #cbd5e1;
			}

			.terrain-emphasis {
				font-weight: 700;
				color: #ffffff;
			}

			.protocol-shell {
				position: relative;
				padding: 4rem 0 5rem;
				background: #020617;
			}

			.protocol-header {
				margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
				max-width: 42rem;
				padding: 0 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.protocol-kicker {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				letter-spacing: 0.24em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #60a5fa;
			}

			.protocol-title {
				margin: 1rem 0 0;
				font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 3rem);
				font-weight: 800;
				line-height: 1.1;
				letter-spacing: -0.03em;
				color: #f8fafc;
				text-wrap: balance;
			}

			.protocol-intro {
				margin: 1rem 0 0;
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.75;
				color: #94a3b8;
			}

			.protocol-grid-layout {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}

			.protocol-card {
				position: relative;
				overflow: hidden;
				border: 1px solid rgba(30, 41, 59, 1);
				border-radius: 1rem;
				background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.5);
				padding: 2rem;
				box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.18);
				backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
				transition:
					transform 0.3s ease,
					border-color 0.3s ease,
					box-shadow 0.3s ease,
					background-color 0.3s ease;
			}

			.protocol-card::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08), transparent 58%);
				opacity: 0;
				transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
				pointer-events: none;
			}

			.protocol-card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-0.5rem);
				border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
				box-shadow:
					0 24px 60px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.3),
					0 20px 50px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.2);
			}

			.protocol-card:hover::before {
				opacity: 1;
			}

			.protocol-card:focus-within {
				border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.65);
				box-shadow:
					0 0 0 4px rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.15),
					0 24px 60px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.3);
			}

			.protocol-card-title {
				margin: 0 0 1rem;
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				line-height: 1.35;
				color: #f1f5f9;
			}

			.protocol-card-copy {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.75;
				color: #94a3b8;
			}

			.support-shell {
				position: relative;
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
				padding: 5rem 1.5rem 6rem;
				background: #020617;
			}

			.support-grid {
				width: min(100%, 74rem);
				margin-inline: auto;
				display: grid;
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}

			.manifesto-card,
			.pillar-panel {
				border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.9);
				border-radius: 1.75rem;
				background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.72);
				padding: 1.75rem;
				box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.35);
				backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
			}

			.manifesto-label,
			.pillar-label {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				letter-spacing: 0.24em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #60a5fa;
			}

			.manifesto-title,
			.pillar-title {
				margin: 1rem 0 0;
				font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 2.4rem);
				font-weight: 800;
				line-height: 1.15;
				letter-spacing: -0.03em;
				color: #ffffff;
				text-wrap: balance;
			}

			.manifesto-copy {
				margin: 1rem 0 0;
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: #cbd5e1;
			}

			.pillar-list {
				margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
				padding: 0;
				list-style: none;
				display: grid;
				gap: 0.9rem;
			}

			.pillar-item {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
				gap: 0.85rem;
				align-items: start;
				border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.85);
				border-radius: 1.1rem;
				background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.5);
				padding: 1rem;
			}

			.pillar-badge {
				display: inline-flex;
				width: 2rem;
				height: 2rem;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				border-radius: 9999px;
				background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.18);
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				font-weight: 800;
				color: #60a5fa;
			}

			.pillar-item strong {
				display: block;
				margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
				color: #f8fafc;
				font-size: 1rem;
			}

			.pillar-item span {
				color: #94a3b8;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			@media (min-width: 768px) {
				.hero-shell {
					padding: 2.5rem;
				}

				.hero-glow--top {
					width: 18rem;
					height: 18rem;
				}

				.hero-glow--bottom {
					right: 6%;
					bottom: 6%;
					width: 14rem;
					height: 14rem;
				}

				.cta-primary {
					padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
					font-size: 1.05rem;
				}

				.terrain-shell {
					padding-top: 8rem;
					padding-bottom: 8rem;
				}

				.protocol-shell {
					padding-top: 4rem;
					padding-bottom: 6rem;
				}

				.protocol-grid-layout {
					grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
				}

				.support-shell {
					padding: 6.5rem 2.5rem 7rem;
				}

				.support-grid {
					grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(18rem, 0.8fr);
					align-items: start;
					gap: 2rem;
				}

				.manifesto-card,
				.pillar-panel {
					padding: 2.25rem;
				}
			}

			@media (min-width: 1200px) {
				.hero-shell,
				.support-shell {
					padding-inline: 4rem;
				}

				.terrain-shell,
				.protocol-header {
					padding-inline: 4rem;
				}
			}

			@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
				html {
					scroll-behavior: auto;
				}

				.cta-primary {
					transition: none;
				}

				.cta-primary:hover {
					transform: none;
				}

				.protocol-card {
					transition: none;
				}

				.protocol-card:hover {
					transform: none;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-slate-950 font-sans text-slate-100 antialiased">
		<main class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-950">
			<section
				class="hero-shell min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-6"
				aria-labelledby="hero-title"
			>
				<div class="hero-bg absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>
				<div class="hero-glow hero-glow--top" aria-hidden="true"></div>
				<div class="hero-glow hero-glow--bottom" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<header class="hero-grid relative z-10 mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-col items-center">
					<p
						class="eyebrow inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-blue-500/20 bg-slate-900/70 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-blue-400 backdrop-blur"
					>
						Chapa Apolo <span aria-hidden="true">•</span> Lançamento CACOMP
					</p>

					<h1
						id="hero-title"
						class="hero-title text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-transparent md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl"
					>
						Um pequeno passo para nós, um grande salto para a Computação do Piauí.
					</h1>

					<h2 class="hero-subtitle mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-400 md:text-xl">
						A missão de fundar o CACOMP começou. O código está aberto.
					</h2>

					<div class="cta-wrap mt-10">
						<a
							href={manifestoHref}
							class="cta-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-blue-600 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-blue-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(37,99,235,0.4)] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-4 focus-visible:ring-blue-400/60 focus-visible:ring-offset-4 focus-visible:ring-offset-slate-950"
						>
							<span>Ler o Manifesto Oficial</span>
							<span aria-hidden="true">📄</span>
						</a>
					</div>
				</header>
			</section>

			<section
				class="terrain-shell bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950 to-slate-900 py-20 md:py-32"
				aria-labelledby="terrain-title"
			>
				<h2 id="terrain-title" class="sr-only">
					O Reconhecimento do Terreno
				</h2>
				<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 text-center">
					<p
						class="terrain-copy max-w-3xl mx-auto text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-300 md:text-2xl"
					>
						O professor entrega uma teoria de excelência. Mas quem organiza os nossos eventos
						de treinamento prático? Quem fecha parcerias com o mercado de tecnologia? Quem
						estrutura os eventos que colocam o nosso curso no mapa?
						<span class="terrain-emphasis text-white font-bold"> A inércia acabou.</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section
				class="protocol-shell py-16"
				aria-labelledby="protocol-title"
			>
				<div class="protocol-header">
					<p class="protocol-kicker text-blue-400">O Protocolo Apolo</p>
					<h2 id="protocol-title" class="protocol-title">
						Propostas objetivas para transformar energia estudantil em estrutura real.
					</h2>
					<p class="protocol-intro">
						Da preparação competitiva ao contato com o mercado, a missão é criar mecanismos
						contínuos de evolução para o curso.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
					<div class="protocol-grid-layout grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8">
						<article
							class="protocol-card rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/50 p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-900/20"
						>
							<h3 class="protocol-card-title mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-slate-100">
								💻 Competições e Treinamentos
							</h3>
							<p class="protocol-card-copy text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
								Rede de apoio tática e estruturação de ligas de treinamento para a Maratona
								SBC e competições de tecnologia.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article
							class="protocol-card rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/50 p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-900/20"
						>
							<h3 class="protocol-card-title mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-slate-100">
								🔬 Pesquisa e Mercado
							</h3>
							<p class="protocol-card-copy text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
								Conectando a base teórica a projetos práticos, organizando eventos de conexão
								com empresas e laboratórios.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article
							class="protocol-card rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/50 p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-900/20"
						>
							<h3 class="protocol-card-title mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-slate-100">
								🛠️ Infra e Sobrevivência
							</h3>
							<p class="protocol-card-copy text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
								Protocolos de monitoria voluntária e mapeamento técnico contínuo para suporte
								aos coordenadores.
							</p>
						</article>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section
				id="manifesto"
				class="support-shell border-t border-slate-800/80 px-6 py-20"
				aria-labelledby="manifesto-title"
			>
				<div class="support-grid mx-auto max-w-5xl gap-8">
					<article class="manifesto-card rounded-3xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-8">
						<p class="manifesto-label text-blue-400">Manifesto Oficial</p>
						<h3 id="manifesto-title" class="manifesto-title text-2xl font-extrabold text-white">
							A Computação do Piauí merece representação, comunidade e futuro.
						</h3>
						<p class="manifesto-copy text-slate-300">
							A Chapa Apolo nasce para fundar o CACOMP com organização, presença institucional
							e abertura real para quem quer construir junto.
						</p>
						<p class="manifesto-copy text-slate-300">
							Nossa proposta é transformar vontade coletiva em ação concreta: defender pautas,
							conectar estudantes e abrir espaço para uma cultura acadêmica mais forte, técnica
							e participativa.
						</p>
					</article>

					<aside class="pillar-panel rounded-3xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-8">
						<p class="pillar-label text-blue-400">Três compromissos</p>
						<h3 class="pillar-title text-2xl font-extrabold text-white">
							O primeiro lançamento já tem rota definida.
						</h3>

						<ul class="pillar-list">
							<li class="pillar-item">
								<div class="pillar-badge" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
								<div>
									<strong>Representar de verdade</strong>
									<span>
										Construir um centro acadêmico presente nas decisões que afetam o curso e os
										estudantes.
									</span>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="pillar-item">
								<div class="pillar-badge" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
								<div>
									<strong>Conectar a comunidade</strong>
									<span>
										Aproximar calouros, veteranos, egressos e oportunidades em uma rede ativa de
										colaboração.
									</span>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="pillar-item">
								<div class="pillar-badge" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
								<div>
									<strong>Executar com transparência</strong>
									<span>
										Abrir o processo, publicar prioridades e criar uma cultura de participação
										contínua.
									</span>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</aside>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
